{"word":"ἐπανέρχομαι","slug":"ἐπανέρχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπανέρχομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ανελεύσομαι</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>but <a href='S:vide'>v.</a> <a href='S:ἐπάνειμι'><el>ἐπάνειμι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> with aor2 and <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a>:— <i>to go back, return</i>, <el>ἐκ τόπου</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:—in writing or speaking, <i>to return to</i> a point, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <i>to recapitulate</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to go up, ascend</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: <i>to go up</i> or <i>pass</i> from one place to another, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}